# NearMe — Location Finder / Nearby Places App

A full-stack Python web app to discover nearby places using **completely free APIs** — no API key required.

---

## 🔧 Tech Stack

| Layer     | Tech                                      |
|-----------|-------------------------------------------|
| Backend   | Python 3 + Flask                          |
| Geocoding | Nominatim (OpenStreetMap) — free, no key  |
| POI data  | Overpass API (OpenStreetMap) — free, no key |
| Map tiles | OpenStreetMap via Leaflet.js — free       |
| Frontend  | Vanilla JS + Leaflet.js                   |

---

## ✨ Features

- 🔍 **Search by address / city / landmark** with autocomplete
- 📍 **Use your current GPS location** (browser geolocation)
- 🗺️ **Interactive map** with clickable markers
- 🏷️ **12 categories**: Food, Health, Hotels, Shopping, Bank/ATM, Education, Parks, Transport, Fuel, Worship, Entertainment, All
- 📏 **Adjustable radius** (200 m – 5 km)
- 📋 **Sorted results** by distance with details panel
- 📞 Phone, website, opening hours, wheelchair info
- 🌐 OpenStreetMap link for every place
- 🖱️ Click anywhere on the map to search that spot
- 📱 Responsive (works on mobile)

---

## 🚀 Quick Start

```bash
# 1. Install dependency (only Flask needed!)
pip install flask

# 2. Run the server
python app.py

# 3. Open in browser
# http://localhost:5000
```

