---

## 🔌 API Endpoints

| Endpoint          | Description                          |
|-------------------|--------------------------------------|
| `GET /`           | Serve the web app                    |
| `GET /api/geocode?q=` | Forward geocode (address → lat/lon) |
| `GET /api/reverse?lat=&lon=` | Reverse geocode (lat/lon → address) |
| `GET /api/nearby?lat=&lon=&radius=&category=` | Nearby places search |
| `GET /api/suggest?q=` | Autocomplete suggestions |

---

## 🗂️ Supported Categories

`all`, `restaurant`, `hospital`, `hotel`, `shopping`, `bank`, `school`, `park`, `transport`, `fuel`, `worship`, `entertainment`

---

## ⚠️ Notes

- Nominatim has a **1 request/second** rate limit — the app respects this for normal use.
- Overpass API is free but may be slow for large radius queries. Radius is capped at 10 km.
- No API keys, no registration, no billing — 100% free and open data.